data.title: ESEA Season 28: Main Division - Europe
data.meta_description: ESEA Season 28: Main Division - Europe is an online European CS:GO tournament organized by ESEA. This C-Tier tournament took place from May 15 to Aug 13 2018 featuring 173 teams competing over a total prize pool of $9,400 USD.
